---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="System Integration | Sentinel Nexus"
  description="Connect AI capabilities to your existing enterprise systems—ERP, CRM, ITSM, and data platforms. We ensure seamless data flow and process orchestration across your technology ecosystem."
>
  <section class="hero-service">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/ai-implementation">AI Implementation</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span>System Integration</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>System Integration</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Connect AI to the Systems That Run Your Business</p>
      <p class="hero-description">
        AI in isolation delivers nothing. We connect your AI capabilities to the enterprise systems that matter—ERP, CRM, ITSM, and data platforms—ensuring seamless data flow, reliable orchestration, and measurable ROI.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>The Integration Challenge</h2>
        <p>
          Most AI initiatives stall not because the models aren't good enough, but because they can't reach the data and systems they need. Enterprise environments are complex—decades of accumulated platforms, custom configurations, siloed databases, and proprietary APIs that were never designed to work with AI.
        </p>
        <p>
          This integration gap is the #1 barrier to AI ROI. A brilliant document processing model is worthless if it can't feed results into your ERP. A predictive analytics engine fails if it can't access real-time CRM data. Agentic workflows break down when they can't orchestrate across your ITSM and ticketing systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          We specialize in bridging this gap—designing and building the integration architecture that lets AI capabilities connect to, reason about, and act across your entire technology ecosystem.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Integration Methodology</h2>

      <div class="characteristics-grid">
        <div class="char-card">
          <div class="char-number">01</div>
          <h3>System Audit and Mapping</h3>
          <p>Inventory your technology landscape end-to-end. Map data flows, dependencies, APIs, authentication methods, and integration points across every system AI needs to touch.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="char-card">
          <div class="char-number">02</div>
          <h3>Integration Architecture Design</h3>
          <p>Design a scalable integration blueprint: API strategies, middleware selection, event-driven patterns, and data transformation layers tailored to your environment and AI requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="char-card">
          <div class="char-number">03</div>
          <h3>API and Connector Development</h3>
          <p>Build custom connectors, adapters, and API wrappers that bridge AI capabilities to enterprise systems—handling authentication, rate limiting, error recovery, and data format translation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="char-card">
          <div class="char-number">04</div>
          <h3>Data Flow Orchestration</h3>
          <p>Implement reliable data pipelines that move information between systems in real-time or batch—with transformation, validation, and conflict resolution built in.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="char-card">
          <div class="char-number">05</div>
          <h3>Testing and Validation</h3>
          <p>Rigorous integration testing across environments: end-to-end data integrity checks, load testing, failover scenarios, and validation against production-equivalent conditions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="char-card">
          <div class="char-number">06</div>
          <h3>Go-Live and Monitoring</h3>
          <p>Phased rollout with comprehensive monitoring: real-time dashboards, alerting, health checks, and runbooks to ensure integrations remain stable and performant in production.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Integration Use Cases</h2>

      <div class="usecases-grid">
        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>ERP Integration</h3>
          <p>Connect AI-driven insights and automation directly to SAP, Oracle, Microsoft Dynamics, and other ERP platforms—enabling intelligent procurement, forecasting, and financial operations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>CRM Intelligence</h3>
          <p>Enrich Salesforce, HubSpot, and other CRM systems with AI-generated insights: lead scoring, churn prediction, next-best-action recommendations, and automated data enrichment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>ITSM Automation</h3>
          <p>Integrate AI with ServiceNow, Jira, and ITSM platforms for intelligent ticket routing, automated diagnostics, predictive incident management, and self-healing infrastructure workflows.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>Data Platform Unification</h3>
          <p>Bridge data warehouses, lakes, and analytics platforms so AI models can access unified, real-time data across Snowflake, Databricks, BigQuery, and on-premise systems.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>Legacy Modernization</h3>
          <p>Wrap legacy systems with modern API layers and event-driven interfaces—unlocking decades of business logic and data for AI consumption without risky rip-and-replace projects.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="usecase-card">
          <h3>Cross-System Orchestration</h3>
          <p>Build multi-system workflows where AI coordinates actions across platforms: quote-to-cash, hire-to-retire, incident-to-resolution—with full visibility and audit trails.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Security and Governance Built In</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Enterprise integration demands enterprise-grade security. Every integration we build embeds security and compliance from the architecture level.</p>

      <div class="characteristics-grid">
        <div class="char-card">
          <h3>Secure Data Flow</h3>
          <p>End-to-end encryption, secure credential management, and data masking ensure sensitive information is protected as it moves between systems and AI services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="char-card">
          <h3>Access Control</h3>
          <p>Role-based and attribute-based access controls enforce least-privilege principles across every integration point, API, and data pipeline.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="char-card">
          <h3>Audit Trails</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive logging of every data movement, transformation, and system interaction—providing full traceability for compliance and incident investigation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="char-card">
          <h3>Compliance Alignment</h3>
          <p>Integration architectures designed to meet SOC 2, HIPAA, GDPR, and industry-specific requirements with built-in data residency and retention controls.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Integration Powers Everything</h2>
        <p>
          System integration is the foundation that makes every other AI capability possible. Without reliable connections to your enterprise systems, AI remains a proof-of-concept. With them, it becomes an operational force multiplier.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our integration work is designed to complement and accelerate your broader AI initiatives—from workflow automation to security and governance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillars-callout">
        <div class="pillar-link">
          <h4>Workflow Automation</h4>
          <p>Once systems are connected, automate the workflows that span them with intelligent, adaptive orchestration.</p>
          <a href="/ai-implementation/workflow-automation-process-redesign">Learn about Workflow Automation &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar-link">
          <h4>AI Security</h4>
          <p>Protect the data flows and API connections that power your AI integrations with enterprise-grade security.</p>
          <a href="/ai-security">Explore AI Security &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to connect your AI capabilities?</h2>
      <p>Let's map your integration landscape and build the connections that turn AI potential into operational reality.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" data-umami-event="{System Integration | Start a Conversation Btn}">Start a Conversation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-service {
    padding: 10rem 0 4rem;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, var(--color-bg) 70%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .hero-service h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-dark {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: -1rem auto 2rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .content-block {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-block p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .characteristics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .char-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .char-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .char-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .char-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .usecases-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .usecase-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .usecase-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
  }

  .usecase-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pillars-callout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .pillar-link {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .pillar-link h4 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pillar-link p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pillar-link a {
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pillar-link a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .section-cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-1) 0%, #1e40af 100%);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-cta p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .section-cta .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-accent-1);
  }

  .section-cta .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f0f0f0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-service {
      padding: 8rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .characteristics-grid,
    .usecases-grid,
    .pillars-callout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
